# Frontend Stack Defaults

- For frontend/UI/client tasks in this repo, use React with Vite unless the user explicitly requests another stack.
- Use TailwindCSS for styling by default; avoid introducing other CSS frameworks unless requested.
- Prefer modern React patterns (functional components, hooks, component composition).
- Keep project structure compatible with standard Vite + React conventions for straightforward local dev and deployment.
- Use environment variables for frontend runtime configuration and never hardcode secrets in client code.
